	<hr>
	<ul> 
		<li><b>Goal:</b> Create a web app that visualizes personalized Spotify statistics across different time ranges using the Spotify Web API.</li>
		<br>
		<li><b>Tools/Tech:</b>JavaScript, React, Spotify API, Netlify, OAuth2</li>
	</ul>
	<br>
	<p>
		This project is a modern React web app that connects to the Spotify Web API to display user-specific listening data such as top tracks and artists 
		across short, medium, and long-term periods. It handles authentication via OAuth2 and uses Netlify serverless functions in place of a full backend.
	</p>
	<br>
	<p>
		The frontend is styled for clarity and responsiveness, offering a simple but interactive interface for exploring your listening habits. 
		Hosted on Netlify.
	</p>
